{"tid":2439476,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"（100%真）琴晚遇到靈異事件","createTime":"2021-03-09T09:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T19:10:23.000Z","uid":370760,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d13bf1ce2d9e428ee3ac0780f98c9b15b57386d7","tid":2439476,"uid":370760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:35:07.000Z","msg":"小弟好細個嗰陣已經係有敏感體質嘅，成日會無啦啦喊，成日訓唔到，最後要老母去廟度求個開咗光嘅護身符比我先叫好番啲（但都係會有感覺）。到而家大個，都係仲有呢個體質，但大不了都係去到某啲地方會全身起雞皮，下意識要走之類小事，冇話直接比我知佢存在，但琴晚真係好癲。<br />\n<br />\n  琴晚去咗女朋友屋企訓，但因為佢同啊妹一間房，所以我要出廳訓，一開始都叫做有啲周身唔聚財，但冇為意繼續訓，訓到凌晨兩點就仆街了，無啦啦個電視自己開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開電視台都叫好啲，佢直接show 個灰色畫面比我睇（唔係connect畫面嗰啲，係真係純灰色），好彩以前跟過個識法嘅人學下嘢，保持到冷靜，當冇事發生走去熄電視繼續瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（因為保持唔到冷靜，人嘅火會細咗，佢就越惡）<br />\n<br />\n  但之後就更仆街，明明冇開窗，好清楚feel到一股冷氣不停「摸」我右半身，係來回摸嗰隻，而冇比佢摸嘅左半身係正常體溫，隨後全身雞皮起到痴線，以我之前嘅經驗，就知道佢唔係一般嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  嗰時基本上已經保持唔到冷靜，意識到啲火一定冇咁旺，呢個時候我決定用師傅教嘅六字大明咒幫幫手，但仆街，好死唔死唔記得咗正音點唸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有唸喃嘸阿彌陀佛頂住先，唸緊嗰陣團冷氣明顯退咗，唸唸下好眼訓，所以停咗。<br />\n<br />\n  點知一停，個電視即刻開番，又係灰畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢刻真係頂唔緊，驚到pk，入女朋友房等天光算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1978d366d6b16efe4515492bc523976c50ad757","tid":2439476,"uid":228438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"你女朋友有冇比你嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16abdadcd334af21cbea87b10d005b3c96ec513f","tid":2439476,"uid":370760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"篇文係係廳打出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc992386e62cf3eb51433732f11f6c83058afe4a","tid":2439476,"uid":370760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1978d366d6b16efe4515492bc523976c50ad757","tid":2439476,"uid":228438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"你女朋友有冇比你嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:39:12.000Z","msg":"佢都知我有呢啲體質，見到我個樣已經知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a88c8dfc1993aa84b12b9968c909084f613f2f4","tid":2439476,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:39:30.000Z","msg":"講故台"},{"pid":"db8d30f7815b86381f298da442519283457da1f8","tid":2439476,"uid":370760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"講大話比人燒春袋，我話嘅"},{"pid":"2de5d55077632db2d93fe5b10ad1423012f4d723","tid":2439476,"uid":10056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"點解幾十年來D鬼都係搞同樣既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開電視 吹氣 開門關門 開燈熄燈"},{"pid":"7c2d38ed2e1b702f972e8e3d73d568bb774f020f","tid":2439476,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5ce25ff21ab5a75be9ef260140826cf926b897","tid":2439476,"uid":370760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2de5d55077632db2d93fe5b10ad1423012f4d723","tid":2439476,"uid":10056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"點解幾十年來D鬼都係搞同樣既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開電視 吹氣 開門關門 開燈熄燈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"有問過點解，因為電子嘢佢哋易控制啲，而物件相對難，靈力要高啲先得"},{"pid":"71a810f9b1d5c5d857c6ec2979577bde615586de","tid":2439476,"uid":370760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c2d38ed2e1b702f972e8e3d73d568bb774f020f","tid":2439476,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f